t her side, Luna learns important coming-of-age lessons: Respect is earned, advice can be deceiving, and adults aren't always right.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/378690/extras/22b1fa7c75fc2721730c827cb5995708.poster.avif?t=1766173923\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/378690/extras/22b1fa7c75fc2721730c827cb5995708.webm?t=1766173923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/378690/extras/22b1fa7c75fc2721730c827cb5995708.mp4?t=1766173923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
